<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Title</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .slr-main {
            padding: 2rem 6rem;
        }

        .slr-main-product-name {
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }

        .slr-main-product-name h2 {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 3rem;
        }

        .slr-main-container {
            width: 100%;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .slr-main-container-left {
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-evenly;
            gap: 2rem;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .slr-main-container-left img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
        }

        .slr-thumbnail-grid {
            display: flex;
            max-width: 50vw;
            gap: 1rem;
            overflow-x: auto;
            padding-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .slr-thumbnail-btn {
            width: 6rem;
            height: 6rem;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
            background: #fff;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.15s ease;
        }

        .slr-thumbnail-btn.locked {
            border-color: #222222 !important;
        }

        .slr-thumbnail-btn:hover {
            border-color: #222222;
        }

        .slr-thumbnail-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        /* 悬停预览样式 */
        .slr-thumbnail-container:hover .slr-hover-preview {
            opacity: 1;
            pointer-events: auto;
        }

        .slr-hover-preview {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 100%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            width: 12rem;
            height: 12rem;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
            opacity: 0;
            pointer-events: none;
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
        }


        .slr-main-container-right {
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 15px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .slr-option-group {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .slr-option-label {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            display: block;
        }

        .slr-option-buttons {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 0.75rem;
        }

        .slr-option-radio {
            display: none;
        }

        .slr-option-btn {
            background: #fff;
            color: #000;
            border: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            transition: all 0.15s ease;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            min-width: fit-content;
        }

        .slr-option-btn:hover {
            border-color: #222222;
        }

        .slr-option-radio:checked + .slr-option-btn {
            background: #222222;
            color: #fff;
            border-color: #222222;
        }

        /* 数量选择器 */
        .slr-quantity-group {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .slr-quantity-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            width: 8rem;
            height: 2.5rem;
            border: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .slr-quantity-btn {
            width: 2.5rem;
            height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border: none;
            background: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
        }

        .slr-quantity-btn:first-child {
            border-right: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .slr-quantity-btn:last-child {
            border-left: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .slr-quantity-input {
            width: 3rem;
            height: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            border: none;
            outline: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }


        .slr-price-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: baseline;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .slr-current-price {
            font-size: 1.875rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #222222;
        }

        .slr-compare-price {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            color: #9ca3af;
            text-decoration: line-through;
        }


        /* 数量选择器 */
        .slr-quantity-group {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .slr-quantity-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            width: 8rem;
            height: 2.5rem;
            border: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .slr-quantity-btn {
            width: 2.5rem;
            height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border: none;
            background: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
        }

        .slr-quantity-btn:first-child {
            border-right: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .slr-quantity-btn:last-child {
            border-left: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .slr-quantity-input {
            width: 3rem;
            height: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            border: none;
            outline: none;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .slr-button-group {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .slr-button-group button {
            padding: 0.8rem 0.6rem;
            border-radius: 0.4rem;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .slr-btn {
            flex: 1;
            height: 3rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.15s ease;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .slr-btn-primary {
            background: #222222;
            color: #eee;
        }

        .slr-btn-primary:hover {
            background: #000;
        }

        .slr-btn-outline {
            background: #eee;
            color: #222222;
            border: 2px solid #222222;
        }

        .slr-btn-outline:hover {
            background: #222222;
            color: #eee;
        }

        .slr-btn-disabled {
            background: #9ca3af;
            color: #fff;
            cursor: not-allowed;
        }

        .slr-delivery-group {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 30px 1fr;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .slr-delivery-group svg {
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
        }

        .slr-delivery-info {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .slr-delivery-info h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .slr-delivery-info p {
            color: #121212;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .slr-delivery-info a {
            color: #121212;
            font-size: 12px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .slr-product-detail {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
        }

        .slr-detail-recommend {
            color: #191919;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .slr-detail-grid {
            width: 100%;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;

        }

        .slr-detail-grid-item {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .slr-detail-grid-icon {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .slr-stroke-width-standard {
            stroke-width: 24px;
        }

        .slr-stroke-width-32 {
            stroke-width: 32px;
        }

        .slr-fill-none {
            fill: none;
        }

        .slr-icon {
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .slr-standard-icon, .slr-custom-icon {
            stroke: rgb(50 126 191);
            fill: rgb(50 126 191);
        }


        .slr-summary-accordion {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.3rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        .slr-detail-summary {
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }

        .slr-summary-accordion-summary {
            width: 100%;
            list-style: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            padding: 1rem 0;
            font-weight: bold;
            position: relative;
        }

        .slr-summary-icon {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .slr-summary-icon svg {
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        .slr-summary-accordion-summary::marker {
            content: "";
        }

        .slr-summary-icon::after {
            content: ">";
            position: absolute;
            right: 16px;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }

        .slr-summary-accordion-summary[open] .slr-summary-accordion-summary::after {
            transform: rotate(90deg);
        }

        .slr-summary-accordion-content {
            padding: 0 16px 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #444;
        }

        .slr-info {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 2rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .slr-info-title {
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .slr-info-title h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .slr-info-poster {
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
        }

        .slr-features-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .slr-feature-item {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .slr-tag {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: gray;
        }

        .slr-number {
            font-size: 6rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: block;
            color: #FF8C00; /* Orange color for number */
        }

        .slr-feature-item p {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }

        /* Styling for different colors on numbers */
        .slr-feature-item:nth-child(2) .slr-number {
            color: #9b4dff; /* Purple color */
        }

        .slr-feature-item:nth-child(3) .slr-number {
            color: #00f9ff; /* Light blue color */
        }

        .slr-poster {
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .slr-poster-container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .slr-poster-container-box {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .slr-poster-container-box .slr-box-tag {
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: gray;
        }

        .slr-poster-container-box .slr-box-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }

        .slr-box {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 4rem;
        }

        .slr-box-question {
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
            font-size: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .slr-box-thing {
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            justify-content: space-evenly;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .slr-box-thing-item {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
        }


        .slr-thing-icon {
            width: 85px;
            height: 85px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #3c3940;
            border-radius: 1rem;
        }

        .slr-thing-icon svg {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
        }

        .slr-thing-icon .slr-standard-icon {
            stroke: #ffffff;
            fill: #ffffff;
        }

        .slr-thing-icon .slr-custom-icon {
            stroke: #ffffff;
            fill: #ffffff;
        }

        .slr-box-banner {
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            justify-content: space-evenly;
            align-items: center;
            background-image: linear-gradient(270deg, rgba(17, 48, 66, 1) 9%, rgba(73, 73, 73, 1) 88%);
            padding: 2rem;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 1rem;
        }

        .slr-box-banner-item {
            max-width: 320px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .slr-box-banner-item h2 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .slr-banner-item-li {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        @media screen and (width <= 64rem) {

            .slr-main {
                padding: 1rem;
            }

            .slr-main-container, .slr-features-container {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 10px;
            }

            .slr-main-container-left {
                padding: 0;
            }

            .slr-poster-container {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 1rem;
            }

            .slr-poster-container-box {
                gap: 5px;
            }

            .slr-box-thing, .slr-box-banner {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 2rem;
            }

            .slr-thumbnail-grid {
                max-width: 80vw;
            }

            .slr-box-thing-item {
                gap: 2px;
            }

            .slr-box-title {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
        }


    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="slr-main">
    <div class="slr-main-product-name">
        <h2>{{ product.title }}</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="slr-main-container">
        <div class="slr-main-container-left">
            <div class="slr-main-image-container">
                {% if product.featured_image %}
                    <img src="{{ product.featured_image | img_url: '800x800' }}"
                         class="slr-main-image" id="slr-main-image"
                         alt="{{ product.featured_image.alt | escape }}">
                {% else %}
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/800x800?text=No+Image"
                         class="slr-main-image" id="slr-main-image" alt="No image available">
                {% endif %}
            </div>
            {% if product.images.size > 1 %}
                <div class="slr-thumbnail-grid">
                    {% for image in product.images %}
                        <div class="slr-thumbnail-container">
                            <button
                                    class="slr-thumbnail-btn {% if forloop.first %}locked{% endif %}"
                                    data-image="{{ image | img_url: '800x800' }}" data-alt="{{ image.alt | escape }}">
                                <img src="{{ image | img_url: '200x200' }}" class="slr-thumbnail-img"
                                     alt="{{ image.alt | escape }}">
                            </button>
                            <!-- 悬停预览 -->
                            <div class="slr-hover-preview">
                                <img src="{{ image | img_url: '400x400' }}" class="slr-thumbnail-img"
                                     alt="{{ image.alt | escape }}">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    {% endfor %}
                </div>
            {% endif %}

        </div>
        <div class="slr-main-container-right">
            {% for option in product.options_with_values %}
                <div class="slr-option-group">
                    <label class="slr-option-label">Choose your {{ option.name }} :</label>
                    <div class="slr-option-buttons">
                        {% for value in option.values %}
                            <div>
                                <input type="radio" name="options[{{ option.name }}]"
                                       id="slr-{{ option.name | handleize }}-{{ value | handleize }}"
                                       value="{{ value }}"
                                       class="slr-option-radio" {% if forloop.first %}checked{% endif %}>
                                <label for="slr-{{ option.name | handleize }}-{{ value | handleize }}"
                                       class="slr-option-btn">
                                    <span>{{ value }}</span>
                                </label>
                            </div>
                        {% endfor %}
                    </div>
                </div>
            {% endfor %}

            <div class="slr-price-container" id="slr-price-container">
                {% assign current_variant = product.selected_or_first_available_variant %}
                {% if current_variant.compare_at_price > current_variant.price %}
                    <span class="slr-current-price" id="slr-current-price">{{ current_variant.price | money }}</span>
                    <span class="slr-compare-price"
                          id="slr-compare-price">{{ current_variant.compare_at_price | money }}</span>
                {% else %}
                    <span class="slr-current-price" id="slr-current-price">{{ current_variant.price | money }}</span>
                {% endif %}
            </div>

            <div class="slr-quantity-group">
                <label class="slr-option-label">{{ settings.quantity_label | default: 'Quantity' }}</label>
                <div class="slr-quantity-container">
                    <button type="button" class="slr-quantity-btn" id="slr-decrease-btn">
                        <i class="ri-subtract-line">-</i>
                    </button>
                    <input type="text" name="quantity" class="slr-quantity-input"
                           value="1" min="1" id="slr-quantity">
                    <button type="button" class="slr-quantity-btn" id="slr-increase-btn">
                        <i class="ri-add-line">+</i>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="slr-button-group">
                {% if product.available %}
                    <button type="button" id="slr-buy-now-btn" class="slr-btn slr-btn-primary">
                        {{ settings.buy_now_text | default: 'Buy Now' }}
                    </button>
                    <button type="button" id="slr-add-to-cart-btn" class="slr-btn slr-btn-outline">
                        {{ settings.add_to_cart_text | default: 'Add to Cart' }}
                    </button>
                {% else %}
                    <button class="slr-btn slr-btn-disabled" disabled>
                        {{ settings.sold_out_text | default: 'Sold Out' }}
                    </button>
                {% endif %}
            </div>

            <div class="slr-delivery-group">
                <svg class="slr-icon  slr-standard-icon" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"
                     xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path d="M0 3.75156C0 3.47454 0.224196 3.24997 0.500755 3.24997H10.647C10.9235 3.24997 11.1477 3.47454 11.1477 3.75156V5.07505V5.63362V6.10938V13.6616C10.9427 14.0067 10.8813 14.1101 10.5516 14.6648L7.22339 14.6646V13.6614H10.1462V4.25316H1.00151V13.6614H2.6842V14.6646H0.500755C0.224196 14.6646 0 14.44 0 14.163V3.75156Z"></path>
                    <path d="M18.9985 8.08376L11.1477 6.10938V5.07505L19.6212 7.20603C19.8439 7.26203 20 7.46255 20 7.69253V14.1631C20 14.4401 19.7758 14.6647 19.4992 14.6647H17.3071V13.6615H18.9985V8.08376ZM11.1477 13.6616L13.3442 13.6615L13.3443 14.6647L10.5516 14.6648L11.1477 13.6616Z"></path>
                    <path d="M7.71269 14.1854C7.71269 15.6018 6.56643 16.75 5.15245 16.75C3.73847 16.75 2.59221 15.6018 2.59221 14.1854C2.59221 12.7691 3.73847 11.6209 5.15245 11.6209C6.56643 11.6209 7.71269 12.7691 7.71269 14.1854ZM5.15245 15.7468C6.01331 15.7468 6.71118 15.0478 6.71118 14.1854C6.71118 13.3231 6.01331 12.6241 5.15245 12.6241C4.29159 12.6241 3.59372 13.3231 3.59372 14.1854C3.59372 15.0478 4.29159 15.7468 5.15245 15.7468Z"></path>
                    <path d="M17.5196 14.1854C17.5196 15.6018 16.3733 16.75 14.9593 16.75C13.5454 16.75 12.3991 15.6018 12.3991 14.1854C12.3991 12.7691 13.5454 11.6209 14.9593 11.6209C16.3733 11.6209 17.5196 12.7691 17.5196 14.1854ZM14.9593 15.7468C15.8202 15.7468 16.5181 15.0478 16.5181 14.1854C16.5181 13.3231 15.8202 12.6241 14.9593 12.6241C14.0985 12.6241 13.4006 13.3231 13.4006 14.1854C13.4006 15.0478 14.0985 15.7468 14.9593 15.7468Z"></path>
                </svg>
                <div class="slr-delivery-info">
                    <h2>
                        Pickup available at Ignite HQ
                    </h2>
                    <p>Usually ready in 2-4 days</p>
                    <a>View store information</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="slr-product-detail">
        <div class="slr-detail-recommend">
            <p class="slr-detail-recommend-title">Discover the innovation and performance of the Edge Pixa 9. Packed
                with the latest technology,
                this smartphone ensures ultra-fast speeds, stunning visuals, and smooth multitasking. Stay
                ahead, capture moments in exceptional detail, and stay connected effortlessly with the Edge Pixa
                9.</p>
            <div>
                <p style="margin: 1rem 0">Source: Google</p>
                <div class="slr-detail-grid">
                    <div class="slr-detail-grid-item">
                        <p>Battery life</p>
                        <div class="slr-detail-grid-icon">
                            <svg class="slr-icon slr-custom-icon" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false"
                                 xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 512 512">
                                <rect x="32" y="144" width="400" height="224" rx="45.7" ry="45.7"
                                      stroke-linecap="square" stroke-miterlimit="10"
                                      class="slr-fill-none slr-stroke-width-standard">
                                </rect>
                                <rect x="85.69" y="198.93" width="292.63" height="114.14" rx="4" ry="4"
                                      stroke-linecap="square" stroke-miterlimit="10"
                                      class="slr-stroke-width-standard">
                                </rect>
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-miterlimit="10" d="M480 218.67v74.66"
                                      class="slr-fill-none slr-stroke-width-standard">
                                </path>
                            </svg>
